Global Fish Oil for Feed Market Insights
Fish Oil for Feed Market size was valued at USD 1.20 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.80 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Fish Oil for Feed Market Overview
The global fish oil for feed market is projected to reach USD 2.62 billion by 2032, exhibiting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.02% during the forecast period from 2024 to 2032. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for sustainable and nutritious feed ingredients in aquaculture and livestock farming. Fish oil, rich in omega-3 fatty acids, plays a crucial role in enhancing the health and growth of animals, thereby supporting the expansion of the market. Recent developments include the adoption of fish oil in pet food formulations to improve pet health and advancements in processing technologies that enhance production efficiency and product quality.

